sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as Group API
    participant Redis as Redis Cache
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Notif as Notification Service
    participant BullMQ as BullMQ Queue

    U->>API: POST /api/v1/groups (create group)
    API->>DB: Validate & create group
    DB-->>API: Group created
    API->>DB: Create groupMember (owner)
    DB-->>API: Member created
    API->>Redis: Cache group data
    Redis-->>API: Cached
    API-->>U: Group created response

    U->>API: POST /api/v1/group-invitations/:id/send-bulk
    API->>DB: Create invitations
    DB-->>API: Invitations created
    API->>BullMQ: Queue email jobs
    BullMQ-->>API: Jobs queued
    API-->>U: Invitations sent

    loop For each invitation
        BullMQ->>Notif: Process email job
        Notif-->>BullMQ: Email sent
    end

    U->>API: POST /api/v1/group-invitations/accept
    API->>DB: Validate token
    DB-->>API: Valid invitation
    API->>DB: Create groupMember
    DB-->>API: Member added
    API->>DB: Update group member count
    API->>Redis: Invalidate caches
    API-->>U: Successfully joined
